":{"label":["Dauer von Bezaubern","Schaden","Abklingzeit"],"effect":["{{ charmduration }} -> {{ charmdurationNL }}","{{ basedamage }} -> {{ basedamageNL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownNL }}"]},"maxrank":3,"cooldown":[130,110,90],"cooldownBurn":"130/110/90","cost":[100,100,100],"costBurn":"100","datavalues":{},"effect":[null,[100,200,300],[4,4,4],[1,1.25,1.5],[0.25,0.25,0.25],[75,75,75],[150,150,150],[150,150,150],[130,110,90],[0,0,0],[0,0,0]],"effectBurn":[null,"100/200/300","4","1/1.25/1.5","0.25","75","150","150","130/110/90","0","0"],"vars":[],"costType":" {{ abilityresourcename }}","maxammo":"-1","range":[150,150,150],"rangeBurn":"150","image":{"full":"RakanR.png","sprite":"spell10.png","group":"spell","x":336,"y":144,"w":48,"h":48},"resource":"{{ cost }} {{ abilityresourcename }}"}],"passive":{"name":"Aufgeplustert","description":"Rakan erhält in regelmäßigen Abständen einen Schild.","image":{"full":"Rakan_P.png","sprite":"passive3.png","group":"passive","x":192,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48}},"recommended":[]}}}